
The sound of her cries and shouts of pain are heard but I don't care. I simply enjoy myself and feed of her and when I done, I let her body fall to the ground.
I licked my lips, taking in any excess blood and then I feel myself calming down. I could feel my skin and eyes settle down into a more normal phase. Well... For now, at least until I find my next victim to feed on.
